these outstanding individuals come from within the ranks of CBS
News journalists.''
   Vieira, who has been on ``West 57th'' since its premiere in
August 1985, came from the CBS Chicago bureau.
   Kroft joined ``West 57th'' in November 1986. Before that, he was
in the CBS London bureau.
